{
  "chapter": 27,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述李寻欢（化装成酒鬼）在孙驼子的小店中等待。店内陆续来了四批客人：蓝衫老人与辫子姑娘、南山双虎韩家兄弟、以紫面少年杨承祖为首的四人组、以及面带青记的瘦长汉子。辫子姑娘以说书为名，讲述李寻欢与阿飞的往事，引起众人注意。青面汉子突然声称有六人将死于此地，并点名白毛猴胡非、大力神段开山、铁枪小霸王杨承祖、水蛇胡媚及韩家兄弟。六人惊恐之际，黄衫少年率众而至，以六枚黄铜制钱控制六人，将其带到店外弄堂站立。随后又有三批黄衫人带着各自的随从到来，店内外气氛凝重如坟墓。全章以神秘势力的压迫感和李寻欢暗中观察为主线，铺垫后续冲突。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "今天看样子又没有客人上门了，还是趁早打烊吧，也好陪你喝两杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "酒鬼",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "别着急，我算定了你今天的买卖必定特别好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "酒鬼",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我会算命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫面少年",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "这位姑娘可是卖唱的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "text": "我不会唱，只会说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫面少年",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "text": "说书，说故事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫面少年",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "那更好了，却不知你会说什么书？后花园才子会佳人？宰相千金抛绣球？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "text": "都不对，我说的是江湖中最轰动的消息，武林中最近发生的大事，保证又新鲜，又紧张。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫面少年",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "妙极妙极，这种事我想在座的诸君都喜欢听的，你快说吧。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "text": "我不会说，我爷爷会说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫面少年",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "你会什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "text": "我只会替爷爷帮腔。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿衣妇人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "要说就快说，飞什么媚眼？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "既然如此，爷爷你就说一段吧，也好赚几个酒钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "你可听说过李寻欢这名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "我当然听说过，不就是那位仗义疏财，大名鼎鼎的小李探花吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“听说，小李飞刀，例不虚发，直到如今为止，还没有一个人能躲开过，这句话不知道是真是假？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“你若不相信，不妨去问问‘平湖’百晓生，去问问五毒童子，你就知道这句话是真是假了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“百晓生和五毒童子岂非早就全都死了么？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“不错，他们都死了，就因为他们不相信这句话。”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“我可不敢不相信这句话，不相信这句话的只怕都是傻瓜。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“只可惜像李寻欢这样的英雄豪杰，如今也已死了。”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“死了？谁有那么大的本事能杀了他！”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“谁也没有那么大的本事，有本事杀他的只有一个人。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“谁？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“就是他自己！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“他自己怎么会杀死自己呢？我看他一定还活在世上。”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“就算他还活在世上，也和死差不多了……哀莫大于心死，可叹呀可叹，可惜呀可惜……”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“除了他之外，还有什么人可称得上是英雄呢？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“你可听说过‘阿飞’这名字？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“好像听说过。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“听说此人剑法之快，举世无双，却不知是真是假？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“伊哭的武功如何？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“兵器谱中，青魔手排名第九，武功自然是好得很了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“铁笛先生、少林心宠、赵正义、田七……这些人的武功又如何？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“这几位都是江湖中一等的高手，谁都知道的。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“阿飞的剑法若不快，这些人怎会败在他剑下？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“如今这位‘阿飞’的人呢？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“他也和小李探花一样，忽然不见了，谁也不知道他的消息，只知道他是和林仙儿同时失踪的。”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“林仙儿？不就是那位号称天下第一美人的林姑娘？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“不错。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“情是何物？偏叫世人都为情苦，而且还无处投诉……”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫面少年",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“闲话少说，书归正传，你说的故事呢？”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_zi_mian_shao_nian",
      "text": "“像阿飞和李寻欢这样的人物，都已不知下落，江湖中还会发生什么大事？我老头子还有什么好说的！”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面瘦长汉子",
      "listener": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "“那倒也不见得。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "text": "“哦？阁下的消息难道比我老头子还灵通？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面瘦长汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“据我所知，不久就要有件惊天动地的事发生了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "text": "“在哪里发生？什么时候发生？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面瘦长汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“就在此时，就在此地！”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿衣妇人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "text": "“我倒看不出此时此地会发生什么了不得的大事。”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面瘦长汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“据我所知，至少有六个人马上就要死在这里！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yi_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "绿衣妇人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "text": "“哪六个人？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面瘦长汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“‘白毛猴’胡非、‘大力神’段开山、‘铁枪小霸王’杨承祖、‘水蛇’胡媚和‘南山双虎’韩家兄弟！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "段开山",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "text": "“你是什么东西？敢在这里胡说八道？”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "段开山",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "text": "“我看你才是一脸倒霉相，休想活得过今天晚上……”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面瘦长汉子",
      "listener": "char_duan_kai_shan",
      "text": "“你以为是我要杀你们？凭你们还不配让我动手，我这只不过是教训教训你们，要你们说话斯文些。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_cheng_zu",
      "speaker_name": "杨承祖",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "text": "“慢走，你倒说说看是谁要杀我们？”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面瘦长汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“要杀你们的人就快来了！……”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面瘦长汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你们反正逃也逃不了的，还是慢慢地等着瞧吧。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_han_ban",
      "text": "“南山双虎的威名，在下是久已仰慕得很了。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ban",
      "speaker_name": "韩斑",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "“不敢。”",
      "tone": "谦逊",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ming",
      "speaker_name": "韩明",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "“胡大侠和胡姑娘兄妹，暗器轻功双绝，我兄弟也久仰得很！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_han_ming",
      "text": "“韩二侠过奖了。”",
      "tone": "谦逊",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_han_ban",
      "text": "“两位若不嫌在下冒昧，就请移驾过去一叙如何？”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ban",
      "speaker_name": "韩斑",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "“在下等也正有此意。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_han_ban",
      "text": "“两位久居关东，在下等却一直在江淮间走动，兄弟实在想不出有什么人会想将我们一网打尽。”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ban",
      "speaker_name": "韩斑",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "“在下正也不解。”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_han_ban",
      "text": "“听那位朋友的口气要杀我们的那人，武功想必极高，我们也许真的不是他敌手，只不过……”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_han_ban",
      "text": "“三个臭皮匠，胜过一个诸葛亮，合我们六人之力，总不至于连还手之力都没有吧。”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ban",
      "speaker_name": "韩斑",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "“胡兄说得好，我们六个也不是木头人，难道就会乖乖地让别人砍脑袋吗？”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ming",
      "speaker_name": "韩明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“常言道：兵来将挡，水来土掩。那人若不来也就罢了，若真的来……嘿嘿……”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“若真的来了，就叫他来得去不得。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫老人",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“朋友若是想喝酒，就坐下来喝两杯吧，我请你。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "“这把戏真好看极了，想不到你原来是个变戏法的，你再变几手给我们瞧瞧好不好？我一定要爷爷请你喝酒。”",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_shao_nian",
      "text": "“你的戏法为什么不变了？我还想看哩。”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面瘦长汉子",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“这种戏法还是少看些为妙。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "text": "“为什么？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面瘦长汉子",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "“你们若是会武功，他方才那两手戏法只怕已将你们变死了。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_shou_chang_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面瘦长汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“一醉解千愁，这话倒真不错，喝醉了的人确实比清醒的占便宜。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 413
    }
